

Dragonfly - Animation Suite

Usage:

var larva : BasicLarva = new BasicLarva( target );
larva
	.xy( 500, 100 )
	.xyscale( 1.5, 1.5 )
	.rotation( 90 )
	.fly( .3, 1, Expo.easeOut )
	.on_start( _start ).on_progress( _progress ).on_complete( _complete );

